        "created_at": "2023-01-09T18:25:11.632Z",
        "cooked": "<p>OK, guess I got the txn API completely wrong. The following should make more sense, but I still don\u2019t get a timeout:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-auto\">import fdb\nfdb.api_version(710)\ndb = fdb.open()\ndb.set(fdb.tuple.pack((1,)), fdb.tuple.pack((2,)))\ntr = db.create_transaction()\ntr.options.set_retry_limit(1)\ntr.options.set_timeout(1000)\nw = tr.watch(fdb.tuple.pack((1,)))\ntr.commit()\nw.wait()\n</code></pre>\n<p>Any suggestion? Thanks a lot!</p>",
